---
layout: base.njk
title: AI Sense
---

<div class="section-hero">
  <div class="dictionary-entry">
    <h1 class="dictionary-word">AI Sense</h1>
    <div class="dictionary-meta">
      <span class="dictionary-phonetic">/ey-eye sens/</span>
      <span class="dictionary-pos">noun</span>
    </div>
    <ol class="dictionary-defs">
      <li>The basic intuitions a person needs before using any AI tool.</li>
      <li>A practical understanding of how AI actually works, what AI can and cannot do, and why the same AI behaves differently in different apps.</li>
    </ol>
    <p class="dictionary-example">"You don't need a PhD in machine learning. You just need AI Sense."</p>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="section" style="margin-top: var(--spacing-8);">
  <div class="section-list">
    {% for item in aisense.statements %}
    <article class="card">
      <a class="card-link" href="{{ ('/' + item.id + '/') | url }}" aria-label="{{ item.statement }}"></a>
      <div class="card-content">
        <div class="card-header">
          <h2 class="card-title">{{ item.statement }}</h2>
        </div>
        <p class="card-excerpt">{{ item.explanation }}</p>
      </div>
    </article>
    {% endfor %}
  </div>
</div>
